name: Godette in Calakmul
description:
Assets employed in this project from OpenGameArt.com: 3TD Cave Pack Pro v1.0 and Nobiax textures.

Godette was modeled with VRoid based on the character created by Andrea Calabró, Alux and Spider made by me.

Godette was animated  with Mixamo.

Sounds are from the GameAudioGDC Bundle.
